            <div type="transcript" id="F38A">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>I never told the buried gold </l>
                    <l>Opon the hill that lies - </l>
                    <l>I saw the sun, his plunder done - </l>
                    <l>Crouch low to guard his prize - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>He stood as near</l>
                    <l>As stood you here - </l>
                    <l>A pace had been between - </l>
                    <l>Did but a snake bisect the brake </l>
                    <l>My life had forfeit been.  </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>That was a wondrous booty.</l>
                    <l>I hope 'twas honest gained -<app type="division"><lem><pb/></lem></app>
 </l>
                    <l>Those were the fairest ingots </l>
                    <l>That ever kissed the spade.  </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Whether to keep the secret - </l>
                    <l>Whether to reveal -</l>
                    <l>Whether while I ponder </l>
                    <l>Kidd may sudden sail - </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Could a shrewd advise me </l>
                    <l>We might e'en divide - </l>
                    <l>Should a shrewd <em>betray</em> me -</l>
                    <l>&quot;Atropos&quot; decide - </l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
